These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-1::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, boat, train, skateboard
1. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the right of the person driving the skateboard##5
2. the person driving the scooter is somewhere to the left of the person driving the train##5
3. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the skateboard and the person driving the boat##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |     3      |  4   |
| Transport   | skateboard | scooter | boat | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, woodworking, puzzles, drawing
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##5
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2    |    3    |       4       |
| Hobby   | fishing | drawing | woodworking | puzzles |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  scientist, doctor, fisherman, freelancer
1. the doctor is on the right of the fisherman##1
2. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
3. the scientist is the scientist##1
4. the scientist is somewhere to the right of the freelancer##5

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | freelancer | scientist | fisherman | doctor |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, fishing, drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |   3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | fishing | drawing | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, zombie, comedy
1. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching comedy movies and the person watching zombie movies##2
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy | comedy | mystery |

