.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, traveling, skydiving, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby   | gardening | traveling | skydiving | board-games |

