.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, scooter, van, tram
1. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the taxi is somewhere to the left of the person driving the scooter##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | taxi | tram | scooter | van |

