.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-5-15::.
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, mouse, horse, rat
1. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the mouse is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the hedgehog##2
3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hedgehog##5
4. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the rat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |    2    |  3   |   4    |
| Pet   | rat | mouse | hedgehog | horse |

